page_title: 'Quickstart: Generate images with Azure OpenAI Service and Azure OpenAI Studio'
page_description: Learn how to generate images with Azure OpenAI Service in the DALL-E playground (Preview) in Azure OpenAI Studio.
chunk_content: Prerequisites#### DALL-E 3- An Azure subscription. Create one for free.- An Azure OpenAI resource created in the `EastUS`, `AustraliaEast`, or `SwedenCentral` region.- Then, you need to deploy a `dalle3` model with your Azure resource. For more information, see Create a resource and deploy a model with Azure OpenAI.#### DALL-E 2 (preview)- An Azure subscription. Create one for free.- An Azure OpenAI resource created in the `EastUS` region. For more information, see Create a resource and deploy a model with Azure OpenAI.---
